## Scenario 8 — Industrial Stormwater MSGP Benchmark Exceedance
##
## Module D (CWA). Multi-Sector General Permit (MSGP) benchmark
## exceedance at a stormwater outfall. MSGP Sector AA (fabricated
## metals) — total zinc benchmark 0.12 mg/L. Benchmarks are NOT
## effluent limits — exceedance triggers MSGP Part 6 corrective-action
## ladder (Tier 1/2/3), not enforcement. EPA-only routing.
##
## Key distinction from Scenario 7: benchmarks drive SWPPP review and
## BMP modification, not 24-hour noncompliance reports.
##
## Baseline triples extracted from ehs-ontology-v3.2.ttl (line 1337).

PREFIX ehs: <http://example.org/ehs-ontology#>
PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#>

ASK {
    ehs:Scenario_StormwaterOutfall_MSGP rdf:type ehs:ContextualComplianceActivation ;
        ehs:triggeredByType       ehs:ChemicalHazard ;
        ehs:hasActionContext      ehs:ProcessingAction ;
        ehs:hasContextCondition   ehs:WaterwayProximity ,
                                  ehs:FullRelease ;
        ehs:activatesFramework    ehs:EPA_Framework .
}
